  "texts": [
    "It predicts a latent code Z L DYN = CausalTransformer(Z BOS, Z 0:L-1) that captures the dynamics given the input sequence history.",
    "For positional information, we apply standard sine-cosine embeddings along spatial dimensions.",
    "In the temporal direction, we omit explicit positional encodings, relying instead on the causal structure to encode temporal ordering implicitly (Kazemnejad et al., 2023).",
    "At inference time, given a target number of steps S, the spatial Transformer generates the final latent frame ẐL in an autoregressive manner over S steps.",
    "Each step selectively predicts a subset of masked tokens, conditioned on the dynamic context Z L DYN = CausalTransformer(Z BOS, Z 0:L-1)."
